# Customer Churn Prediction using Machine Learning

## Objective
Predict whether a telecom customer will churn using machine learning.

## Technologies Used
- Python
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Scikit-Learn
- XGBoost
- Matplotlib
- Seaborn

## Models Used
- Logistic Regression
- Random Forest
- XGBoost

## Results
- Achieved around 85-89% accuracy.
- Identified important factors affecting customer churn.

## Dataset
IBM Telco Customer Churn Dataset

